  "text": "Looking ahead to the coming decades with the human population rapidly expanding, the need for food and other resources will continue to grow. The need for pest control will also grow in time. It is my view that pesticide use worldwide could be reduced 50% and still achieve effective pest control [CITATION_1] .",
